divs: Sighting DetailsI was out on the flight line at the Houma Airport taking pictures of helicopters in the morning mist. Examining the picture later I noticed what seems to be two contrails of objects moving from right to left. One (the lower) seems to be generated by a disc-shaped cloud. The other seems to be generated by something in the clouds that has a row of lights. I took this photo myself with a new digital camara and it has not been altered in any way. I insist on exclusive ownership of this photo and it cannot be reproduced without my permission. The more I look at it the harder it is for me to think that it is a natural phenomena.
Summary: Attached picture seems to show two disc shaped objects with contrails
